    <article class="article">
      <header class="article-header">
        <h1 title="想變更pixiv的信箱或密碼" class="article-title">
          想變更pixiv的信箱或密碼
          
        </h1>

        
      </header>

      <section class="article-info">
        <div class="article-content">
          <div class="article-body"><p>若想變更信箱地址或密碼，請登入後於上方選單的「<a href="http://www.pixiv.net/setting_user.php" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">設定</a>」中變更。</p>
<p><a href="https://www.pixiv.net/setting_mail_address.php" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">於此處變更信箱</a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.pixiv.net/setting/password/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">於此處變更密碼</a><br>密碼長度為6至72字元，可使用英數字(a-zA-Z0-9)與符號 (=+*:;!|$&amp;%#@~.,?_"&amp;#'(){}[]&lt;&gt;^/\)。</p></div>

          <div class="article-attachments">
            <ul class="attachments">
              
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

